author: @salonglosswoodstock5773
content: To her credit she was actually singing. She forgot to grab the microphone one night and thr song started but there were no lyrics until she ran across the stage to grab it. I attended 2 shows and 1 I was right at the stage and could hear her singing into the mic. I seriously don't know why people continue to say she lip syncs.
